"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        Register request payloads with different managed objects.
        """
a = payloads.RegisterRequestPayload(managed_object=secrets.Certificate(
    certificate_type=enums.CertificateType.X_509, certificate_value=self.
    certificate_value))
b = payloads.RegisterRequestPayload(managed_object=secrets.Certificate(
    certificate_type=enums.CertificateType.PGP, certificate_value=self.
    certificate_value))
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
